equation.firstDerivative: -((A - B) * D * E * pow(x, E - 1)) / pow((C + D * pow(x, E)), 2)
equation.secondDerivative: ((A - B) * D * E * pow(x, E - 2) * (C - C * E + D * (1 + E) * pow(x, E))) / pow((C + D * pow(x, E)), 3)

equation.firstDerivative: -(A * C * exp(C * (x + D))) / pow((B + exp(C * (x + D))), 2)
equation.secondDerivative: (A * pow(C, 2) * exp(C * (x + D)) * (exp(C * (x + D)) - B)) / pow((exp(C * (x + D)) + B), 3)

equation.firstDerivative: -(A * C * E * exp(C * (x + D)) * pow((B + exp(C * (x + D))), -1 - E))
equation.secondDerivative: (A * pow(C, 2) * E * exp(C * (x + D)) * pow((B + exp(C * (x + D))), -2 - E) * (-B + exp(C * (x + D)) * E))

equation.firstDerivative: -A * B * C * exp(B * exp(C * (x + D)) + C * (x + D))
equation.secondDerivative: -A * B * pow(C, 2) * exp(B * exp(C * (x + D)) + C * (x + D)) * (1 + B * exp(C * (x + D)))

equation.firstDerivative: A * B * C * exp(B * exp(C * (x + D)) + C * (x + D))
equation.secondDerivative: A * B * pow(C, 2) * exp(B * exp(C * (x + D)) + C * (x + D)) * (1 + B * exp(C * (x + D)))

equation.firstDerivative: (C * exp(D + C * x) * (-exp(A) + exp(B))) / ((-1 + exp(D) + exp(C * x)) * (-exp(A) + exp(B + D) + exp(A + C * x)))
equation.secondDerivative: (pow(C, 2) * exp(D + C * x) * (exp(A) - exp(B)) * (-exp(A) + exp(A + D) + exp(B + D) - exp(B + 2 * D) + exp(A + 2 * C * x))) / (pow((-1 + exp(D) + exp(C * x)), 2) * pow((-exp(A) + exp(B + D) + exp(A + C * x)), 2))
equation.equation: A + B + log(-1 + exp(D) + exp(C * x)) - log(-exp(A) + exp(B + D) + exp(A + C * x))

equation.firstDerivative: -((A - B) * D * E * F * pow(x, E - 1) * pow((C + D * pow(x, E)), -1 - F))
equation.secondDerivative: (A - B) * D * E * F * pow(x, E - 2) * pow((C + D * pow(x, E)), -2 - F) * (C - C * E + D * (1 + E * F) * pow(x, E))
equation.equation: (A - B) / pow((C + D * pow(x, E)), F) + B
